### Test Product CRUD với isActive field

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@token = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Login để lấy token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Create Product - Test với đầy đủ fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max Test",
  "slug": "iphone-15-pro-max-test",
  "description": "Test product với đầy đủ fields",
  "price": 29990000,
  "listPrice": 34990000,
  "image": "https://example.com/iphone-15-pro-max.jpg",
  "images": [
    "https://example.com/iphone-1.jpg",
    "https://example.com/iphone-2.jpg"
  ],
  "brand": "Apple",
  "stock": 50,
  "categoryId": "CATEGORY_ID_HERE",
  "specs": {
    "ram": "8GB",
    "storage": "256GB",
    "color": "Titan Tự Nhiên"
  },
  "badges": ["Trả góp 0%", "Mới 100%"],
  "installment": true,
  "isActive": true
}

### 3. Update Product - Test toggle isActive
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isActive": false
}

### 4. Update Product - Test với images
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "image": "https://new-url.com/main.jpg",
  "images": [
    "https://new-url.com/1.jpg",
    "https://new-url.com/2.jpg",
    "https://new-url.com/3.jpg"
  ]
}

### 5. Get Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
